{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2022/07/04/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"redecentralize/alternative-internet","categoryHTML":"<h2>Collaborative Web Editors</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://WikiSuite.org/\">WikiSuite</a>: While Wikipedia is the broadest unified body of knowledge, WikiSuite is the most comprehensive and integrated Open Source enterprise solution. WikiSuite is especially suited to knowledge-centric organizations and offers most (80%+) of the data and information management features all organizations need. Key components include <a href=\"https://wikisuite.org/Virtualmin\">Virtualmin</a>, <a href=\"https://wikisuite.org/Tiki-Wiki-CMS-Groupware\">Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware (aka TikiWiki)</a>, <a href=\"https://wikisuite.org/Jitsi-Meet\">Jitsi Meet</a>, <a href=\"https://wikisuite.org/MeshCentral\">MeshCentral</a>, <a href=\"https://wikisuite.org/Syncthing\">Syncthing</a> and <a href=\"https://wikisuite.org/Manticore-Search\">Manticore Search</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T21:45:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"redecentralize/alternative-internet","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud and storage</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://peergos.org/\">Peergos</a> is a peer-to-peer and end-to-end encrypted global filesystem with fine-grained access control. Provides a secure and private space online where you can store, share and view your photos, videos, music and documents. Also includes a calendar, news feed, task lists, chat and email client. Open source licensed. Can be self-hosted.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T18:13:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"redecentralize/alternative-internet","categoryHTML":"<h2>Collaborative Web Editors</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hackmdio/codimd\">CodiMD</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hackmdio/codimd\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">8.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":8131,\"repo\":\"hackmdio/codimd\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> is a collaborative Editor based on Markdown. CodiMD is the free software version of HackMD, pads are shared via URL and provide additional functionality like editing permissions based on login status and a presentation mode (with reaveal.js).</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T18:13:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"redecentralize/alternative-internet","categoryHTML":"<h2>Networking</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/skycoin/skywire\">Skywire</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/skycoin/skywire\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">62</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":62,\"repo\":\"skycoin/skywire\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> is the Skycoin Project's communication primitive (analogous to MPLS, open-flow, TOX, mesh networking, darknet, i2p) that facilitates mesh networking both on traditional internet service provider infrastructure, and on individually owned wifi and radio equipment, allowing for a phased, incentivized approach to decentralization. <a href=\"https://medium.com/skycoin/skywire-the-new-internet-for-the-new-world-6d09a8542c50\">Skywire Overview</a> | <a href=\"https://skycoin.net/\">skycoin.net</a></li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T18:13:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"redecentralize/alternative-internet","categoryHTML":"<h2>Social Networks</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://getaether.net/\">Aether</a> Reddit-like communities run on a p2p network that hides your IP.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T18:13:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"redecentralize/alternative-internet","categoryHTML":"<h2>Dead</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.dendr.io/\">Dendrio</a> is a video distribution network that leverages the peer to peer WebRTC protocol to transfer website content between browsers.  This allows us to make data downloads faster for users but without any installation requirements.  For website owners, we are trivial to set up, and are transparent to existing CDN setups.  Our technology is geared towards streaming video and we support a multitude of different video formats and players.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T18:13:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"agamm/awesome-developer-first","categoryHTML":"<h2>Reports Generation</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://docraptor.com\">DocRaptor</a> - HTML to PDF API built specifically for Paged Media using the <a href=\"https://www.princexml.com/\">Prince</a> PDF library.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T17:17:09.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"zoidbergwill/awesome-ebpf","categoryHTML":"<h1>eBPF in Security</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/h3xduck/TripleCross\">TripleCross</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/h3xduck/TripleCross\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.2k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1189,\"repo\":\"h3xduck/TripleCross\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A Linux eBPF rootkit with a backdoor, C2, library injection, execution hijacking, persistence and stealth capabilities.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T16:14:11.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-selfhosted/awesome-selfhosted","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h3>Miscellaneous</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/almarklein/mypaas\">MyPaas</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/almarklein/mypaas\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">260</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":260,\"repo\":\"almarklein/mypaas\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Run your own PaaS using Docker, Traefik, and great monitoring. <code>BSD-2-Clause</code> <code>Python/Docker</code></li>","updatedAt":"2022-07-04T14:32:01.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-selfhosted/awesome-selfhosted","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h3>Search Engines</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zincsearch.com\">ZincSearch</a> - A lightweight alternative to elasticsearch that requires minimal resources, written in Go. (<a href=\"https://github.com/zinclabs/zinc#playground-server\">De